file_content.text: I don't know what you're talkin' about. If I had spice, you'd have found it already.
I don't know about that. Good spice trader can get past a simple search.
Maybe he swallowed it. We could cut him open, see what's inside.
No! Okay, I was dealing, but I'll clear out! You'll never see me again!
You do that. And tell your friends. No spice in Justicar territory.
